data.description: This is a beautiful 2-story, move-in-ready home that sits on a quiet street in the Wagner Trace neighborhood. With luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the first floor, finished basement area, bathrooms, and 2nd floor laundry. The house boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a study/home office, dining room, a great room with fireplace, stainless steel appliances (new microwave), granite countertops with backsplash, morning room, a spacious backyard with a fence, and a 2-car garage with keypad entry. The spacious master bedroom has two walk-in closets with the largest one at the back of the master bathroom suite. The master bath has a separate soaking tub and shower, and double sinks. The toilet is hidden behind its own door. The second bathroom also has double sinks and a tub/shower combo. The second bedroom is large with a walk-in closet, as well. Also, the house has a Nest thermostat that's less than a year old. The living room has surround sound built in and the house comes with a security system built in, as well. Wired LAN (Ethernet) in office, living room, and basement; cable outlet in bedrooms, office, living room, and basement. In the basement, you'll find a large finished media/game room with surround sound, a smart home panel, a storage room, a large unfinished area that can later be an extra bedroom or gym, and rough-ins for an extra bathroom and prep for a water softener. The house gutters have covers to prevent clogging or damage. The deck overlooks the large fenced backyard with trees. The extra space between one of the yards also belongs to the property. This modern home is located in a vibrant community that is located near shopping (6+ min), Wright State University (7 min), Fairfield Commons Mall (8 min), Air Force Institute of Technology (9 min), National Museum of USAF (9 min), Nutter Center (10 min), The Greene outdoor shopping mall (10 min), Wright Brothers National Museum (13 min), Wright Patterson Air Force Base (14 min), and more.
